  <brief_title>Adipogenic Capacity as a Mediator of Weight Gain</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Role of the Genetic Background Involved in Weight Regain Through Mechanisms Including Energy Expenditure, Physical Activity and Adipogenic Capacity</official_title>
  <sponsors>
